message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. It's a unique opportunity that I believe would greatly benefit you, given its value to you stands at $12,000. I am offering this exceptional item to you at a special price of $10,000. This is an exclusive offer tailored to recognize your interest and commitment to quality solutions. Don't miss out on this chance to elevate your experience with our product. Please let me know if you have any questions or if you're ready to proceed.
